---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import { profile } from "@/settings";
---

<Layout title={`Teaching | ${profile.fullName}`}>
  <div class="prose max-w-none">
    <h1>Resources</h1>

    <blockquote>On this page you can find information and links to various open-source and community resources I have produced, such as software and tooling, teaching resources, and other materials for running workshops or facilitating discussions.</blockquote>

    <h2>Turing Commons</h2>

    <img src="/images/hero.png" alt="Illustration of a smart city with a central skyscraper linked by dotted lines to icons depicting autonomous vehicles, sustainable energy, and digital communication. Peripheral circles show interactions like a virtual handshake, medical diagnostics, and satellite communication, emphasizing a connected, tech-integrated urban environment." /> {/* Adjusted image path */}

    <p>The <a href="https://alan-turing-institute.github.io/turing-commons" class="link">Turing Commons</a> is an online platform I created, in collaboration with others at the Alan Turing Institute, to support open dialogue and reflection about the responsible design, development, and deployment of data-driven technologies. On this platform you can find a range of freely available teaching materials, including the following courses:</p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-8 not-prose">
      <div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-sm">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title">Responsible Research and Innovation</h3>
          <p class="text-base-content/80 text-sm">Learn about the principles and practices of responsible research and innovation in data science and AI.</p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end mt-4">
            <a href="https://alan-turing-institute.github.io/turing-commons/rri/index.html" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary" target="_blank">View Course</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-sm">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title">Public Engagement of Data Science and AI</h3>
          <p class="text-base-content/80 text-sm">Discover effective methods for engaging the public in data science and AI research and applications.</p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end mt-4">
            <a href="https://alan-turing-institute.github.io/turing-commons/ped/index.html" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary" target="_blank">View Course</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-sm">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3 class="card-title">AI Ethics &amp; Governance</h3>
          <p class="text-base-content/80 text-sm">Explore the ethical and governance challenges of AI systems and approaches to addressing them.</p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-end mt-4">
            <a href="https://alan-turing-institute.github.io/turing-commons/aeg/index.html" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary" target="_blank">View Course</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</Layout>